NaviCharaList.name: Folon
NaviCharaList.description:
A serious and energetic fairy of time.
Apparently her cherished watch
has a big secret.

NaviCharaList.name: Rene
NaviCharaList.description:
A fairy of time who loves history.
She is said to be very scared if you
interrupt her reading.

NaviCharaList.name: Astoria
NaviCharaList.description:
A fairy of time who loves to fight.
She says she never misses a training
session in case of emergency.

NaviCharaList.name: Myas
NaviCharaList.description:
A carefree and easy-going fairy of time.
Her mysterious bag is said to be
full of treasures.
